kpi_info.title: period_duration
kpi_info.use: Duration of the measurement period in minutes.

kpi_info.title: ifOutOctets_EF
kpi_info.use: The total number of octets transmitted by the interface, including framing characters, using Expedited Forwarding PHB class. This counter is available only on AXCF and IFUH units. UPDATED: The counter is updated when an octet is transmitted within the PHB class.

kpi_info.title: ifOutPackets_EF
kpi_info.use: The number of outbound packets that were successfully transmitted within the Expedited Forwarding PHB class. This counter is available only on AXCF and IFUH units. UPDATED: The counter is updated when a packet is transmitted within the PHB class.

kpi_info.title: ifOutDroppedOctets_EF
kpi_info.use: The number of outbound octets within the Expedited Forwarding PHB class that were dropped in the IP scheduler due to congestion. This counter is available only on AXCF and IFUH units. UPDATED: The counter is updated when an octet needs to be dropped due to congestion within the PHB class.

UPDATED: The counter is updated when a packet needs to be dropped due to congestion within the PHB class.
